criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient ≥ 18 years;

          -  Available data of Pdi and PNC;

          -  Suspected unilateral diaphragmatic paralysis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Abnormalities in thoracic wall which susceptible to modify the investigation's
             results;

          -  Scoliosis;

          -  Pleural effusion.
